0s1",{"id":333,"name":334,"alternativeText":18,"caption":18,"width":335,"height":336,"formats":337,"hash":344,"ext":79,"mime":82,"size":345,"url":346,"previewUrl":18,"provider":55,"provider_metadata":18,"createdAt":347,"updatedAt":347,"documentId":348,"publishedAt":58},578,"Joost websitefoto.png",278,326,{"thumbnail":338},{"ext":79,"url":339,"hash":340,"mime":82,"name":341,"path":18,"size":342,"width":343,"height":215},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/thumbnail_Joost_websitefoto_af5f8633d8.png","thumbnail_Joost_websitefoto_af5f8633d8","thumbnail_Joost websitefoto.png",18.83,133,"Joost_websitefoto_af5f8633d8",23.92,"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/Joost_websitefoto_af5f8633d8.png","2024-03-08T12:44:24.321Z","ja3uxwy59jyctja6btxtsrja",[],[351,356,359,362,365,368,370,421],{"__component":352,"id":353,"title":18,"asideText":354,"underline":122,"centered":122,"blankAside":122,"aside":18,"content":355,"introductionText":18},"global.pagesection",348,"","Om deze invoegtoepassing te kunnen gebruiken, heb je op zijn minst een actief Power BI account en [gratis licentie](https://learn.microsoft.com/nl-nl/power-bi/enterprise/service-admin-licensing-organization) nodig.\n\nAlles om ons heen is in beweging. Zo ook jouw data. Wanneer je de laatste getallen wilt tonen in een belangrijke presentatie, wil je liever niet de data tonen van een half uur geleden d.m.v. een afbeelding, maar direct live kunnen inzien.  \n\nAls je een Power BI rapportage dia wilt maken heb je de link (URL) van de Power BI pagina nodig. Deze link kan je vervolgens invoegen in de nieuwe bijgekomen Power BI optie in het Lint van PowerPoint. Nadat het rapport is opgehaald zie je deze direct terug in de presentatie.",{"__component":352,"id":357,"title":18,"asideText":354,"underline":122,"centered":122,"blankAside":122,"aside":18,"content":358,"introductionText":18},349,"![](https://www.sharevalue.nl/images/sharevalue/blogs/Blog_Joost_GIF_inserting-power-bi-add-in.gif)",{"__component":352,"id":360,"title":18,"asideText":354,"underline":122,"centered":122,"blankAside":122,"aside":18,"content":361,"introductionText":18},350,"## Conclusie\n\nVandaag de dag is PowerPoint al een krachtige oplossing om je resultaten te presenteren. Of je nu de jaarcijfers van de lokale voetbalvereniging wil presenteren of de kwartaalcijfers met je werknemers wilt doornemen. Met deze integratie van Live Power BI rapporten ben je in staat om dit nog verder uit te breiden en kan je tijdens het presenteren de data van verschillende kanten bekijken en analyseren.",{"__component":352,"id":363,"title":18,"asideText":354,"underline":122,"centered":122,"blankAside":122,"aside":18,"content":364,"introductionText":18},351,"Wil je meer weten over deze functionaliteit of over het Power Platform in het algemeen, neem dan gerust contact op met ons zodat we de mogelijkheden kunnen bespreken.",{"__component":366,"id":367,"title":18,"showBlankAside":70},"global.social-sharing",60,{"__component":369,"id":129,"name":18,"jobTitle":18},"strapi.author-card",{"__component":93,"id":371,"title":372,"aside":18,"postType":96,"limit":97,"expertise":373},29,"Lees ook onze andere berichten",[374],{"id":61,"title":62,"subTitle":63,"description":64,"shortDescription":65,"slug":66,"createdAt":67,"updatedAt":68,"publishedAt":69,"isCoreExpertise":70,"documentId":71,"image":375,"blocks":378,"midPageBlocks":385,"seo":416},{"id":73,"name":74,"alternativeText":18,"caption":18,"width":75,"height":76,"formats":376,"hash":86,"ext":79,"mime":82,"size":87,"url":88,"previewUrl":18,"provider":55,"provider_metadata":18,"createdAt":89,"updatedAt":89,"documentId":90,"publishedAt":58},{"thumbnail":377},{"ext":79,"url":80,"hash":81,"mime":82,"name":83,"path":18,"size":84,"width":50,"height":85},[379,382],{"__component":93,"id":94,"title":95,"aside":18,"postType":96,"limit":97,"expertise":380},[381],{"id":61,"title":62,"subTitle":63,"description":64,"shortDescription":65,"slug":66,"createdAt":67,"updated